{% doc %}
  @prompt
    Awesome — now right below that SafeSnow intro section, build the next section: a clean Apple-style collection carousel for SafeSnow products. This section sits on a white background (because the previous section fades into white). Keep it premium/minimal: lots of whitespace, crisp typography, no clutter.
    
    Structure:
    
    A small header row at the top of the section:
    
    Left: title like ‘Shop SafeSnow’ (or ‘New Season Picks’)
    
    Under it (or to the right on desktop): one short subtitle like ‘Snowboards, boots & bindings — curated for GCC riders.’
    
    Right side: a simple ‘View all’ link.
    
    Under that: a horizontal carousel of product cards.
    
    Carousel behavior (mobile-first):
    
    Swipeable on mobile with smooth momentum.
    
    On desktop: show left/right arrows (subtle), and allow trackpad scrolling.
    
    Snap scrolling (each card snaps cleanly into place).
    
    Show partial next card peeking (so it’s obvious you can swipe).
    
    Don’t make it too tall — compact and clean.
    
    Card design (Apple-style):
    
    White cards on white section, but with soft shadow + rounded corners.
    
    Product image is the hero (big, centered, consistent aspect ratio).
    
    Under image: product title (1–2 lines max), then price.
    
    Optional tiny label/tag (e.g., ‘New’ / ‘Best Seller’) but only if available—don’t force it.
    
    On hover (desktop): tiny lift + shadow increase (subtle).
    
    Entire card is clickable. Keep it fast.
    
    Data source / Shopify:
    
    Pull products from a selected Shopify collection (make collection a theme setting).
    
    Respect availability: if sold out, show ‘Sold out’ in a subtle way (not red/ugly).
    
    Use the same font system and spacing rules as the intro section.
    
    Keep everything scoped so it doesn’t affect other sections.
    
    Controls / settings:
    
    Settings for: section title, subtitle, collection picker, number of products to show, and toggle arrows on desktop.
    
    Keep the aesthetic consistent with the SafeSnow intro: clean, premium, snowy but not cheesy (no extra snow here—let the product photography do the work).”**, Stop showing products. This carousel is NOT a product carousel. It’s a collection carousel only. I want users to swipe through SafeSnow collections (Snowboards / Boots / Bindings / Apparel / Accessories), and each slide is just the collection card (image + name). No product grids, no product titles, no prices, nothing.
    
    Layout rules:
    
    It must be a horizontal swipe carousel (left/right), not vertical stacking.
    
    On iPhone, it must always show 2 collection cards side-by-side in the viewport (two columns visible at once), and you swipe horizontally to reveal the next ones.
    
    Cards must be the same height, clean spacing, and snap scrolling so it lands neatly.
    
    Show a tiny “peek” of the next card if possible, but always keep 2 visible.
    
    Collection card design (Apple style):
    
    Card is clickable and opens that collection page.
    
    Use the collection featured image as the main visual (centered, consistent crop).
    
    Overlay or below the image: the collection title only (short, clean).
    
    Optional tiny subtitle is okay but keep it minimal (or omit).
    
    Rounded corners, subtle shadow, lots of whitespace. Premium, not busy.
    
    Data source:
    
    Use a list of collections I choose in the section settings (a “collection list” / blocks, where each block = one collection).
    
    Do NOT auto-pull products from the collection. Just pull the collection image + title + URL.
    
    Fix the current issue:
    
    Remove the vertical layout completely (no ‘collection 1 under collection 2’).
    
    Remove any product rendering logic entirely.
    
    Implement true horizontal scrolling with snapping, and enforce 2-up layout on mobile.”**, “Looks good visually — now it needs the actual carousel mechanics. Right now it’s just a static 2-column grid. Turn it into a real horizontal swipe carousel.
    
    On iPhone: keep 2 cards visible at all times, but make the container horizontally scrollable (overflow-x: auto), with touch swipe enabled.
    
    Add scroll snapping so it locks cleanly into position as you swipe (scroll-snap-type: x mandatory and each card scroll-snap-align: start).
    
    Make it feel iOS-native: momentum scrolling (-webkit-overflow-scrolling: touch), hide the scrollbar, and allow swipe/drag.
    
    Keep the spacing and card sizes exactly the same — just make it scroll left/right to reveal more collections.
    
    Desktop: add subtle left/right arrows (optional) OR at least support trackpad horizontal scroll. If you add arrows, they should scroll by exactly one card width.
    
    Also ensure it doesn’t accidentally scroll vertically — it should clearly behave like a horizontal slider.
    
    In short: same design, but convert it from a fixed grid into a swipeable, snapping horizontal carousel.”**
{% enddoc %}
{% assign ai_gen_id = block.id | replace: '_', '' | downcase %}

{% style %}
  .ai-collection-carousel-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    display: block;
    background-color: #ffffff;
    padding: 80px 0;
    width: 100%;
  }

  .ai-collection-carousel__container-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    max-width: {{ settings.max_page_width }}px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 40px;
  }

  .ai-collection-carousel__header-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: flex-end;
    margin-bottom: 48px;
    gap: 24px;
  }

  .ai-collection-carousel__header-left-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    flex: 1;
  }

  .ai-collection-carousel__title-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    font-family: {{ settings.type_heading_font.family }}, {{ settings.type_heading_font.fallback_families }};
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: 32px;
    line-height: 1.2;
    color: #1d1d1f;
    margin: 0 0 8px 0;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
  }

  .ai-collection-carousel__subtitle-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    font-family: {{ settings.type_base_font.family }}, {{ settings.type_base_font.fallback_families }};
    font-weight: 400;
    font-size: 16px;
    line-height: 1.5;
    color: #6e6e73;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .ai-collection-carousel__carousel-wrapper-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    position: relative;
    margin: 0 -40px;
    padding: 0 40px;
  }

  .ai-collection-carousel__track-container-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    overflow-x: auto;
    overflow-y: hidden;
    -webkit-overflow-scrolling: touch;
    scrollbar-width: none;
    -ms-overflow-style: none;
    scroll-behavior: smooth;
    scroll-snap-type: x mandatory;
    touch-action: pan-x;
    cursor: grab;
  }

  .ai-collection-carousel__track-container-{{ ai_gen_id }}:active {
    cursor: grabbing;
  }

  .ai-collection-carousel__track-container-{{ ai_gen_id }}::-webkit-scrollbar {
    display: none;
  }

  .ai-collection-carousel__track-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    display: flex;
    gap: 16px;
    padding: 4px 0;
    width: max-content;
  }

  .ai-collection-carousel__card-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    flex: 0 0 auto;
    width: calc((100vw - 80px - 16px) / 2);
    max-width: 300px;
    scroll-snap-align: start;
    scroll-snap-stop: always;
    background: #ffffff;
    border-radius: 18px;
    box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);
    transition: all 0.3s cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.2, 1);
    text-decoration: none;
    display: block;
    overflow: hidden;
    min-height: 280px;
  }

  .ai-collection-carousel__card-{{ ai_gen_id }}:hover {
    box-shadow: 0 8px 24px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.12);
    transform: translateY(-4px);
  }

  .ai-collection-carousel__image-wrapper-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    position: relative;
    width: 100%;
    padding-bottom: 120%;
    background: #f5f5f7;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .ai-collection-carousel__image-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    object-fit: cover;
  }

  .ai-collection-carousel__placeholder-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    background: #f5f5f7;
  }

  .ai-collection-carousel__placeholder-{{ ai_gen_id }} svg {
    width: 60%;
    height: 60%;
    opacity: 0.3;
  }

  .ai-collection-carousel__content-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    padding: 20px;
  }

  .ai-collection-carousel__collection-title-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    font-family: {{ settings.type_base_font.family }}, {{ settings.type_base_font.fallback_families }};
    font-weight: 600;
    font-size: 18px;
    line-height: 1.3;
    color: #1d1d1f;
    margin: 0;
    display: -webkit-box;
    -webkit-line-clamp: 2;
    -webkit-box-orient: vertical;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .ai-collection-carousel__collection-subtitle-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    font-family: {{ settings.type_base_font.family }}, {{ settings.type_base_font.fallback_families }};
    font-weight: 400;
    font-size: 14px;
    line-height: 1.4;
    color: #6e6e73;
    margin: 6px 0 0 0;
    display: -webkit-box;
    -webkit-line-clamp: 1;
    -webkit-box-orient: vertical;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .ai-collection-carousel__nav-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    position: absolute;
    top: 50%;
    transform: translateY(-50%);
    width: 44px;
    height: 44px;
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.95);
    border: none;
    border-radius: 50%;
    box-shadow: 0 2px 12px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15);
    cursor: pointer;
    display: none;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    transition: all 0.2s ease;
    z-index: 2;
    backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
  }

  .ai-collection-carousel__nav-{{ ai_gen_id }}:hover {
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 1);
    box-shadow: 0 4px 16px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
  }

  .ai-collection-carousel__nav-{{ ai_gen_id }}:disabled {
    opacity: 0.3;
    cursor: not-allowed;
  }

  .ai-collection-carousel__nav--prev-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    left: 8px;
  }

  .ai-collection-carousel__nav--next-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    right: 8px;
  }

  .ai-collection-carousel__nav-{{ ai_gen_id }} svg {
    width: 20px;
    height: 20px;
    fill: #1d1d1f;
  }

  .ai-collection-carousel__empty-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    text-align: center;
    padding: 60px 20px;
    color: #86868b;
    font-family: {{ settings.type_base_font.family }}, {{ settings.type_base_font.fallback_families }};
    font-size: 16px;
  }

  @media (min-width: 750px) {
    .ai-collection-carousel__title-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      font-size: 40px;
    }

    .ai-collection-carousel__subtitle-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      font-size: 17px;
    }

    .ai-collection-carousel__carousel-wrapper-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
    }

    .ai-collection-carousel__card-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      width: 280px;
    }

    {% if block.settings.show_arrows %}
      .ai-collection-carousel__nav-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
        display: flex;
      }
    {% endif %}
  }

  @media (min-width: 990px) {
    .ai-collection-carousel-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      padding: 100px 0;
    }

    .ai-collection-carousel__header-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      margin-bottom: 56px;
    }

    .ai-collection-carousel__card-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      width: 320px;
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 749px) {
    .ai-collection-carousel__container-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      padding: 0 20px;
    }

    .ai-collection-carousel-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      padding: 60px 0;
    }

    .ai-collection-carousel__header-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: flex-start;
      margin-bottom: 32px;
    }

    .ai-collection-carousel__title-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      font-size: 28px;
    }

    .ai-collection-carousel__subtitle-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      font-size: 15px;
    }

    .ai-collection-carousel__carousel-wrapper-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      margin: 0 -20px;
      padding: 0 20px;
    }

    .ai-collection-carousel__track-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      gap: 12px;
    }

    .ai-collection-carousel__card-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      width: calc((100vw - 40px - 12px) / 2);
      min-height: 240px;
    }

    .ai-collection-carousel__image-wrapper-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      padding-bottom: 110%;
    }

    .ai-collection-carousel__content-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      padding: 16px;
    }

    .ai-collection-carousel__collection-title-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      font-size: 16px;
    }

    .ai-collection-carousel__collection-subtitle-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      font-size: 13px;
    }
  }
{% endstyle %}

<collection-carousel-{{ ai_gen_id }} class="ai-collection-carousel-{{ ai_gen_id }}" {{ block.shopify_attributes }}>
  <div class="ai-collection-carousel__container-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
    <div class="ai-collection-carousel__header-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
      <div class="ai-collection-carousel__header-left-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
        {% if block.settings.title != blank %}
          <h2 class="ai-collection-carousel__title-{{ ai_gen_id }}">{{ block.settings.title }}</h2>
        {% endif %}
        {% if block.settings.subtitle != blank %}
          <p class="ai-collection-carousel__subtitle-{{ ai_gen_id }}">{{ block.settings.subtitle }}</p>
        {% endif %}
      </div>
    </div>

    {% if block.settings.collections.size > 0 %}
      <div class="ai-collection-carousel__carousel-wrapper-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
        <button
          class="ai-collection-carousel__nav-{{ ai_gen_id }} ai-collection-carousel__nav--prev-{{ ai_gen_id }}"
          aria-label="Previous collections"
          disabled
        >
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
            <path d="M15.41 7.41L14 6l-6 6 6 6 1.41-1.41L10.83 12z"/>
          </svg>
        </button>

        <div class="ai-collection-carousel__track-container-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
          <div class="ai-collection-carousel__track-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
            {% for collection in block.settings.collections %}
              <a
                href="{{ collection.url }}"
                class="ai-collection-carousel__card-{{ ai_gen_id }}"
              >
                <div class="ai-collection-carousel__image-wrapper-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
                  {% if collection.featured_image %}
                    <img
                      src="{{ collection.featured_image | image_url: width: 800 }}"
                      alt="{{ collection.featured_image.alt | default: collection.title | escape }}"
                      class="ai-collection-carousel__image-{{ ai_gen_id }}"
                      loading="lazy"
                      width="800"
                      height="960"
                    >
                  {% elsif collection.image %}
                    <img
                      src="{{ collection.image | image_url: width: 800 }}"
                      alt="{{ collection.image.alt | default: collection.title | escape }}"
                      class="ai-collection-carousel__image-{{ ai_gen_id }}"
                      loading="lazy"
                      width="800"
                      height="960"
                    >
                  {% else %}
                    <div class="ai-collection-carousel__placeholder-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
                      {{ 'collection-1' | placeholder_svg_tag }}
                    </div>
                  {% endif %}
                </div>

                <div class="ai-collection-carousel__content-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
                  <h3 class="ai-collection-carousel__collection-title-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
                    {{ collection.title }}
                  </h3>
                  {% if block.settings.show_product_count and collection.products_count > 0 %}
                    <p class="ai-collection-carousel__collection-subtitle-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
                      {{ collection.products_count }} 
                      {% if collection.products_count == 1 %}
                        product
                      {% else %}
                        products
                      {% endif %}
                    </p>
                  {% endif %}
                </div>
              </a>
            {% endfor %}
          </div>
        </div>

        <button
          class="ai-collection-carousel__nav-{{ ai_gen_id }} ai-collection-carousel__nav--next-{{ ai_gen_id }}"
          aria-label="Next collections"
        >
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
            <path d="M8.59 16.59L10 18l6-6-6-6-1.41 1.41L13.17 12z"/>
          </svg>
        </button>
      </div>
    {% else %}
      <div class="ai-collection-carousel__empty-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
        Add collections to display in the carousel
      </div>
    {% endif %}
  </div>
</collection-carousel-{{ ai_gen_id }}>

<script>
  (function() {
    class CollectionCarousel{{ ai_gen_id }} extends HTMLElement {
      constructor() {
        super();
        this.trackContainer = this.querySelector('.ai-collection-carousel__track-container-{{ ai_gen_id }}');
        this.track = this.querySelector('.ai-collection-carousel__track-{{ ai_gen_id }}');
        this.prevButton = this.querySelector('.ai-collection-carousel__nav--prev-{{ ai_gen_id }}');
        this.nextButton = this.querySelector('.ai-collection-carousel__nav--next-{{ ai_gen_id }}');
        this.cards = this.querySelectorAll('.ai-collection-carousel__card-{{ ai_gen_id }}');
        this.isDragging = false;
        this.startX = 0;
        this.scrollLeft = 0;
      }

      connectedCallback() {
        if (!this.trackContainer || !this.track) return;

        this.setupNavigation();
        this.setupDragScroll();
        this.updateButtonStates();
      }

      setupNavigation() {
        if (this.prevButton) {
          this.prevButton.addEventListener('click', () => this.scroll('prev'));
        }

        if (this.nextButton) {
          this.nextButton.addEventListener('click', () => this.scroll('next'));
        }

        this.trackContainer.addEventListener('scroll', () => {
          this.updateButtonStates();
        });
      }

      setupDragScroll() {
        this.trackContainer.addEventListener('mousedown', (e) => {
          this.isDragging = true;
          this.startX = e.pageX - this.trackContainer.offsetLeft;
          this.scrollLeft = this.trackContainer.scrollLeft;
          this.trackContainer.style.scrollBehavior = 'auto';
        });

        this.trackContainer.addEventListener('mouseleave', () => {
          this.isDragging = false;
          this.trackContainer.style.scrollBehavior = 'smooth';
        });

        this.trackContainer.addEventListener('mouseup', () => {
          this.isDragging = false;
          this.trackContainer.style.scrollBehavior = 'smooth';
        });

        this.trackContainer.addEventListener('mousemove', (e) => {
          if (!this.isDragging) return;
          e.preventDefault();
          const x = e.pageX - this.trackContainer.offsetLeft;
          const walk = (x - this.startX) * 2;
          this.trackContainer.scrollLeft = this.scrollLeft - walk;
        });
      }

      scroll(direction) {
        const cardWidth = this.cards[0]?.offsetWidth || 0;
        const isMobile = window.innerWidth < 750;
        const gap = isMobile ? 12 : 16;
        const scrollAmount = cardWidth + gap;

        if (direction === 'prev') {
          this.trackContainer.scrollBy({
            left: -scrollAmount,
            behavior: 'smooth'
          });
        } else {
          this.trackContainer.scrollBy({
            left: scrollAmount,
            behavior: 'smooth'
          });
        }
      }

      updateButtonStates() {
        if (!this.prevButton || !this.nextButton) return;

        const scrollLeft = this.trackContainer.scrollLeft;
        const maxScroll = this.trackContainer.scrollWidth - this.trackContainer.clientWidth;

        this.prevButton.disabled = scrollLeft <= 1;
        this.nextButton.disabled = scrollLeft >= maxScroll - 1;
      }
    }

    customElements.define('collection-carousel-{{ ai_gen_id }}', CollectionCarousel{{ ai_gen_id }});
  })();
</script>

{% schema %}
{
  "name": "Collection carousel",
  "tag": null,
  "settings": [
    {
      "type": "header",
      "content": "Content"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "title",
      "label": "Title",
      "default": "Shop SafeSnow"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "subtitle",
      "label": "Subtitle",
      "default": "Explore our curated collections"
    },
    {
      "type": "collection_list",
      "id": "collections",
      "label": "Collections",
      "limit": 12
    },
    {
      "type": "header",
      "content": "Display options"
    },
    {
      "type": "checkbox",
      "id": "show_product_count",
      "label": "Show product count",
      "default": false
    },
    {
      "type": "checkbox",
      "id": "show_arrows",
      "label": "Show arrows on desktop",
      "default": true
    }
  ],
  "presets": [
    {
      "name": "Collection carousel"
    }
  ]
}
{% endschema %}
